<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,330,1284,1309]" pageId="3" pageNumber="82">Bionomics.</emphasis>
All specimens of the 
<typeStatus box="[580,628,1285,1309]" pageId="3" pageNumber="82">type</typeStatus>
series were collected with a Malaise trap in an arid zone dominated by 
<taxonomicName box="[151,274,1321,1345]" class="Liliopsida" family="Agavaceae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="3" pageNumber="82" phylum="Magnoliophyta" rank="family">Agavaceae</taxonomicName>
